    "title": "How to Customize Watch Face Colors on Your Garmin Watch",
    "summary": "Learn how to change and customize watch face colors on your Garmin watch. This guide covers both built-in and Connect IQ watch faces, helping you personalize your device’s appearance and improve visibility in any environment.",
    "slug": "how-to-customize-garmin-watch-face-colors",
