    "title": "How to Remove a Watch Face from Your Garmin Device",
    "summary": "This article explains three easy ways to remove a watch face from your Garmin device — directly on the watch, via the Garmin Connect IQ app, or through Garmin Express on your computer. Whether you’re freeing up storage or switching to a new Wristo design, these steps make managing your watch faces simple and fast.",
    "slug": "remove-watch-face-en",
