    "title": "How to Keep Garmin Watch Connected to Connect IQ",
    "summary": "Learn how to keep your Garmin watch connected to Connect IQ by ensuring Bluetooth stability, syncing apps, and allowing background activity.",
    "slug": "how-to-keep-garmin-watch-connected-to-connect-iq",
    "url": "/en/blog/how-to-keep-garmin-watch-connected-to-connect-iq",
    "lang": null,
    "translations": [
      {
        "lang": "en",
        "slug": "how-to-keep-garmin-watch-connected-to-connect-iq",
        "url": "/en/blog/how-to-keep-garmin-watch-connected-to-connect-iq",
        "title": "How to Keep Garmin Watch Connected to Connect IQ",
        "summary": "Learn how to keep your Garmin watch connected to Connect IQ by ensuring Bluetooth stability, syncing apps, and allowing background activity.",
        "contentHtml": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Your Garmin watch connects to your phone through the Garmin Connect app and installs third-party apps via the Connect IQ platform. To maintain a stable connection between your watch and Connect IQ, follow these steps:</p><h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">1. Ensure Bluetooth Connection Is Stable</h3><ul><li style=\"text-align: left;\">Turn on your phone’s Bluetooth.</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">In the Garmin Connect app, confirm the device shows as “Connected” (not “Syncing” or “Disconnected”).</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"> If connection issues occur, try selecting “Forget Device” and pair again.</li></ul><h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">2. Install and Use the Connect IQ App</h3><ul><li style=\"text-align: left;\">Download the Garmin Connect IQ app (iOS or Android) from the App Store or Google Play.</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">Log in with the same account used for Garmin Connect.</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">Make sure your watch model supports the apps you want to install.</li></ul><h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">3. Sync Connect IQ Content to the Watch</h3><ul><li style=\"text-align: left;\">In the Connect IQ app, select the watch faces, apps, or data fields you want to install.</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">Tap “Install,” and Connect IQ will prompt you to sync.</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">While your watch remains connected via Bluetooth, the content will sync automatically.</li></ul><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.wristo.io/product/e2223d568ec3403d9ea5dec6d8b4f57b/original.jpg\" alt=\"1762084644687.jpg\" data-href=\"https://cdn.wristo.io/product/e2223d568ec3403d9ea5dec6d8b4f57b/original.jpg\" style=\"width: 30%;\"></p><h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">4. Keep Background Permissions and Disable Battery Optimization</h3><ul><li style=\"text-align: left;\">On Android: go to <strong>Settings &gt; Apps &gt; Connect IQ &gt; Battery &gt; Don’t optimize battery usage</strong>.</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">On iOS: make sure both <strong>Garmin Connect</strong> and <strong>Connect IQ</strong> apps are allowed to run in the background.</li></ul><h3></h3>"
      },
      {
        "lang": "zh",
        "slug": "garmin-watch-connect-iq-stable-connection",
        "url": "/zh/blog/garmin-watch-connect-iq-stable-connection",
        "title": "如何保持佳明手表与 Connect IQ 稳定连接",
        "summary": "如何保持佳明手表与 Connect IQ 稳定连接",
        "contentHtml": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">佳明手表可以通过 Garmin Connect App 与手机连接，同时通过 Connect IQ 平台安装第三方应用。要确保手表与 Connect IQ 保持良好的连接，请参考以下步骤：</p><h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">1. <strong>确保手表与手机蓝牙连接正常</strong></h3><ul><li style=\"text-align: left;\">打开手机蓝牙。</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">在 Garmin Connect App 中确认设备已连接（状态是“已连接”而不是“正在同步”或“断开”）。</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">遇到连接问题时，可以尝试“忘记设备”并重新配对。</li></ul><h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">2. <strong>安装并使用 Connect IQ 应用</strong></h3><ul><li style=\"text-align: left;\">下载 Garmin Connect IQ 应用（iOS 或 Android）： App Store Google Play</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">登录与 Garmin Connect 相同的账号。</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">确保你手表的型号支持你想要下载的应用。</li></ul><h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">3. <strong>同步 Connect IQ 内容到手表</strong></h3><ul><li style=\"text-align: left;\">通过 Connect IQ 应用选择想要安装的表盘、应用、数据字段等。</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">点击“安装”后，Connect IQ 会提示同步。</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">手表保持蓝牙连接状态下，内容就会自动同步过去。</li></ul><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.wristo.io/product/e2223d568ec3403d9ea5dec6d8b4f57b/original.jpg\" alt=\"1762084644687.jpg\" data-href=\"https://cdn.wristo.io/product/e2223d568ec3403d9ea5dec6d8b4f57b/original.jpg\" style=\"width: 30%;\"></p><h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">4. <strong>保持后台运行权限和电池优化排除</strong></h3><ul><li style=\"text-align: left;\">在 Android 手机上： 设置 &gt; 应用 &gt; Connect IQ &gt; 电池 &gt; 不优化电池使用。</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">在 iOS 手机上： 保证 Garmin Connect 和 Connect IQ 应用允许后台运行。</li></ul><h3></h3>"
      }
    ],
