    "summary": "Give your Garmin smartwatch a fresh look and express your unique style! This article walks you through how to install and manage custom watch faces via the Connect IQ™ Store — whether you're a new Garmin user or a seasoned pro, you'll master it in minutes.",
    "slug": "use-install-guide-en",
