    "title": "Technical Explanation of Garmin Heart Rate Measurement",
    "summary": "Garmin’s Elevate™ Optical Heart Rate System combines:  ● Optical PPG sensors  ● Motion sensors (accelerometer + gyroscope)  ● Temperature sensors  ● A digital signal processor (DSP) and proprietary algorithms It estimates HR (Heart Rate) and HRV (Heart Rate Variability) from light absorption changes in capillaries.",
